{
  "stem": "13469.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Obviously we could see that each step was a step backwards-- deteriorating kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But nobody really resisted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody tried to get out of it or not be on the list or not be deported as much as they could, but there was never any joint action in any kind of way against all the rules because they were introduced in such a step by step fashion.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody always said, well, we've lived with all this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Just this extra bit that we have to be at home at night between 8:00 and 6:00 isn't really [INAUDIBLE] We usually are anyway kind of thing, so we'll put up with it.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then next month, we're not allowed to shop except between 3:00 and 5:00, and we say, well, it's bad, but we can probably put up with it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in that way, the screw was turned all the time, and we put up with it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If in one go they'd started off by doing everything at once, there probably would have been a big resistance, not only by the Jews but the Dutch would probably have helped us kind of thing, and something would be done.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But in all these ways, the Germans were extremely clever and efficient and methodical.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we succumbed, and we just did what they asked us to do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So more and more people were deported from Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We noticed it at the schools.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Eventually, for example, the whole old age home, the [INAUDIBLE]-- one day, everybody who was in the [INAUDIBLE] was deported to camp-- this [? transit ?] camp called Westerbork in the eastern part of Holland.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We'd heard about that everybody was going there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't know what was happening there and where people went from there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they went in early 1943.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
